WEBVTT

00:00.109 --> 00:02.367
<i>Kenny: Whoever said
that time heals wounds</i>

00:02.443 --> 00:04.289
<i>clearly never got dumped.</i>

00:04.712 --> 00:06.745
<i>Ever since Brett broke up with me,</i>

00:06.846 --> 00:09.981
<i>the world has stopped turning,
the birds have gone quiet.</i>

00:10.084 --> 00:11.817
<i>Even the leaves have wilted away.</i>

00:11.919 --> 00:14.052
<i>I mean, it's winter, but still.</i>

00:14.154 --> 00:18.256
<i>I feel raw, like I'm trapped
in an early '90s music video.</i>

00:18.358 --> 00:19.925
