Where are you taking Eileen tonight?

03:09.997 --> 03:12.330
Oh, no, I'm spending
the evening with mother.

03:12.432 --> 03:14.332
We're gonna dust off the old Slanket

03:14.434 --> 03:16.468
and relive the magic that was "iCarly."

03:16.570 --> 03:19.170
